      <h1>Reference Request - Pastoral/Character (optional) </h1> 
      <fieldset> 
       <legend>New Reference</legend> Click "Create New Reference" below to create and send a recommendation form to your reference. 
       <ol> 
        <li> <label></label> <input type="submit" value="Create New Reference" name="0.9.1.5.0"> </li> 
       </ol> 
      </fieldset> 
      <fieldset> 
       <legend>Monitor and Manage Existing Reference</legend> 
       <p> 1. After you submit a new reference request you will recieve an email with a link to this page with the current status of the request <br><br>2. Status of <strong>waiting</strong>: While the reference is processing your form the status will be "waiting." If the reference does not recieve an email from Westmont, then you may click the <strong>resend</strong> link. This will open your initial request. You may resend as is, or edit as needed before resending. <br><br>3. Status of <strong>complete</strong>: Once a reference has responded the status will be "complete." You may click the email link. This will open your email program to send a thank you email to the reference. </p> 
